<p><strong>Q1: What is the key focus of the book?</strong>
<strong>A:</strong> The 3rd edition of "Strategic Management" explores the latest trends and advancements in the field of strategic management. It emphasizes the importance of aligning an organization's strategy with its internal and external environment, and provides a step-by-step framework for formulating and implementing effective strategies.</p>
<p><strong>Q2: What are the major topics covered in the book?</strong>
<strong>A:</strong> The book covers a wide range of topics, including the strategic planning process, industry analysis, competitive strategy, corporate governance, and innovation. It also discusses the impact of technology, globalization, and sustainability on strategic management decisions.</p>
